{
  "stem": "24130.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The train was going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess they were bombed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they didn't have-- though they were standing here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they're going back and standing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nobody told us where we going, what we doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when we ca-- we arrived to Auschwitz, we saw Auschwitz again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, we were already familiar with the place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had some bread with us, because we-- in the morning, before the [? say ?] appell, we got the bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had the bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we couldn't eat it, because we didn't have any water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So all we wanted is water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got off the train, there was like-- in Auschwitz-- like polluted water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we start running to that water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they start shooting people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We ran anyhow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then they stopped shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A few people were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we, we still went to the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that water was polluted, so we blew up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It, It seems that it didn't agree with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we got undressed again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we came back in front of Mengele.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The first time, we didn't know about Mengele, because we never heard of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We never heard of selections.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't-- But the second time when we came there, we heard already about Mengele and the selections.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So when we came in front Mengele, we were undressed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he saw big stomachs, so he says to us in Hungarian-- he spoke Hungarian, Mengele-- he says, are you pregnant?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We says, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We're not pregnant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We-- so he let us go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We, we went this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then they took us in front of the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew that we going to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
